snippet.title: ONE PIECE ODYSSEY — Water Seven Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
While citizens live and work in the city above, outlaws and monsters lurk in the labyrinthine sewers below. Explore Water Seven and learn more about the grand adventure ahead!

#ONEPIECEODYSSEY pulls into port January 13th, 2023.
